#: .\hr\views.py:274
msgid ""
"Payroll management ensures accurate and timely compensation for staff,\n"
"        covering salary computation, approvals, and payment tracking — "
"providing\n"
"        administrators with clear insight into staff costs, accountability,\n"
"        and effective financial planning."
