#: .\hr\views.py:332
msgid ""
"Payroll transactions record the actual disbursement of staff salaries,\n"
"        capturing payment dates, methods, and references — ensuring "
"traceability,\n"
"        accountability, and accurate financial records for effective "
"payroll\n"
"        auditing and reporting."
